computeAndSetDuration

public void computeAndSetDuration(boolean setLogoutToNowIfNull)
Compute and set the duration, based on logout time

The parameter logoutTime has to be set first. Otherwise, if it is found null it will be set to the current time in order to compute a duration.

Parameters:
setLogoutToNowIfNull - true to set logoutTime to current time if it is null
